have been <PB N="59" REF="68"> the <HI>Dutch</HI> Soldier; but the Difficulty
was, <HI>how</HI> to <HI>prove</HI> it.</P> 
<P>THEY lay in the &s;ame Room; and, at Night, when they were in Bed,
the Blind Man began, under Pretence of Friend&s;hip and Confidence, to
