the <HI>other fifty</HI> in the &s;ame Place, to Morrow; only I am de&s;irous
to be &s;atisfy'd, Whether, in Point of <HI>Con&s;cience,</HI> &s;uch a
Practice is <HI>unlawful?</HI> My Relations being &s;o extravagant, that they
